easy-se (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * easy_se_cli with KEY=VALUE config + SE_* env var support.
  * systemd template unit easy-se@.service with LoadCredential= for the
    profile password.
  * TLS server-cert validation enabled by default (system CA store).

